{"tid":786479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回顧原文】當大衆傳媒講「香港關係法」講到㷫熻熻，有幾點好值得睇返畀Trump封公開信原文係點寫","createTime":"2018-08-20T03:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T15:48:24.000Z","uid":131691,"like":299,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"b2489a82e235cb601f18a14956963d77ce9c288c","tid":786479,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:06:03.000Z","msg":"「商經局帶頭港獨」基本上係封公開信想帶出嘅重點之一：「一國大於一切、中港融合」同埋「美國特別對待香港」嘅矛盾，但係封信有好多細節好似都被輿論忽略或者直情扭曲咗。以下係暫時我搵到嘅，大家如果搵到更多可以補充：<br />\n<br />\n（民族黨Facebook page post咗原文嘅link：PDF版 <a href=\"https://my.mixtape.moe/unuhli.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.mixtape.moe%2Funuhli.pdf&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=6ce32427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://my.mixtape.moe/unuhli.pdf</a> ， 純文字版 <a href=\"https://pastebin.com/xyBnd1GD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpastebin.com%2FxyBnd1GD&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=a38fec12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pastebin.com/xyBnd1GD</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n1. 「民族黨想破壞香港經濟」？<br />\n原文第15點：<br />\n15. In particular, the suspension means that all the tariff and trade policies against China shall equally apply to Hong Kong.  <span style=\"color: red;\">In consideration that China has been exploring ways to evade tariffs through the special status given to Hong Kong, application of the same tariff and trade policies to Hong Kong would also be the most effective measure against such evasion.</span><br />\n其實民族黨係想堵塞中國利用香港嚟繞過關稅。<br />\n<br />\n2. 「踢中國及香港出世貿根本唔應該同美國講」？<br />\n原文第18點：<br />\n18. We therefore believe that revocation of China&rsquo;s WTO membership is to the benefit of both the United States and the civilised world.  <span style=\"color: red;\">The White House&rsquo;s recent suggestion to kick China out of WTO therefore receives our full support.</span><br />\n其實民族黨係和應緊7日前白宮話想踢中國出世貿<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/news/white-house-we-may-have-to-kick-china-out-of-the-wto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonexaminer.com%2Fnews%2Fwhite-house-we-may-have-to-kick-china-out-of-the-wto&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=fd9c3eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/news/white-house-we-may-have-to-kick-china-out-of-the-wto</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r-alUBNk8KE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dr-alUBNk8KE&d=4T8dbDUuPIXk%2FVoA3xnEsR4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=8c337f59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r-alUBNk8KE</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 「民族黨今次想攬抄」？<br />\n原文第20點（逐句翻譯）:<br />\n20. It may appear surprising that we invite you and the United States government under your presidency to adopt measures against the interest of Hong Kong.<br />\n我哋邀請你同埋美國政府用呢啲方法制裁香港，可能你會覺得奇怪。<br />\n-<br />\nHowever, it is <span style=\"color: red;\">both China and the present Chinese-colonial regime of Hong Kong which would in fact suffer the most</span> under the above suggested measures.<br />\n但係現實係：<span style=\"color: red;\">中國同埋香港現時嘅中國殖民政府先至會係受打擊最大</span>。<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">For the local Hong Kong citizens to be empowered and a genuinely autonomous Hong Kong to flourish, both China and the present regime of Hong Kong, </span>who are the enemies of civilisation and fundamental rights, <span style=\"color: red;\">have to be first knocked down.</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果香港本土嘅市民要真正得到權力，令到一個真正自治嘅香港可以蓬勃發展，就一定要首先推冧中國同埋現時香港政權</span>，因爲佢哋都係文明同埋基本權利嘅敵人。<br />\n-<br />\nIt is our sincere belief that <span style=\"color: red;\">a free Hong Kong without Chinese sovereignty is most effective to maintain this only common-law financial hub in East Asia with its function and value to the capitalist world, and to restore a mutually beneficial relationship between the United States and Hong Kong.</span><br />\n我哋堅決相信，<span style=\"color: red;\">一個冇中國主權，一個自由嘅香港係對保持呢個喺東亞唯一一個運行普通法嘅商業中心對資本主義世界嘅價值嘅最有效方法，而咁做亦都係重建美國及香港之間互利關係嘅最有效方法。</span><br />\n<br />\n如果有睇封信嘅內容，就會知道民族黨佢哋根本唔係想攬抄爲目的，而係想中短時期傷害香港嘅同時將中國經濟玩死，幫美國（甚至整個資本主義世界）圍堵中國，從而建立一個冇中國主權嘅自由香港。個方向根本唔係自殺式襲擊，而係對準個「政權」regime打。"},{"pid":"f4e4c4320bc75e09d011f55a7074f03cf8d67e86","tid":786479,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec05549a6627f0301684928685f603d9b68ade9","tid":786479,"uid":14918,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:08:36.000Z","msg":"醫癌細胞就要做化療打毒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7648b8a666a6116a4852abe4bbcc4486eeaa6f00","tid":786479,"uid":191271,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:10:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 高質"},{"pid":"7b3855eb2fe33a502fc7a79645018151f70968d6","tid":786479,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1ccc21566ee73e97bdf67092447fabfb76e68e","tid":786479,"uid":131691,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"quote":{"pid":"7ec05549a6627f0301684928685f603d9b68ade9","tid":786479,"uid":14918,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:08:36.000Z","msg":"醫癌細胞就要做化療打毒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T03:17:23.000Z","msg":"最慘係有班人寧願生cancer都唔想甩頭髮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或甚至以爲可以同個ca